import React from 'react'
import { Form, Input, Label } from 'semantic-ui-react'

const WaterQualityInput = () => (
    <Form>
        <Form.Field>
            <Label>Qualidade da Agua</Label>
            <Input fluid
                placeholder='...'
            />
        </Form.Field>
    </Form>
)

export default WaterQualityInput
